1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Yuanzhao, You're Going To Get A Stye)

4
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,070
Father,

5
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:00,920
it's time for your medicine.

6
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,560
I'll take care

7
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,760
of affairs of state.

8
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,710
You can focus on recovering.

9
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,070
Tell me the truth.

10
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,870
Was He's death

11
00:01:22,430 --> 00:01:24,840
your doing?

12
00:01:25,430 --> 00:01:27,040
The dead cannot be brought back to life.

13
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,230
Father,

14
00:01:29,150 --> 00:01:30,280
please accept my condolences.

15
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,640
I...

16
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:44,280
I truly underestimated you.

17
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:49,000
You actually had the heart
to kill your own brother.

18
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,560
Wasn't your heart just as cruel, Father?

19
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:55,150
You claimed to love my mother,

20
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,150
yet you had her executed for the throne.

21
00:01:58,310 --> 00:02:00,040
I thought I was favored

22
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,310
because you felt

23
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,760
guilty toward me.

24
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:07,790
But all along, you used me
as my elder brother's whetstone.

25
00:02:07,790 --> 00:02:08,710
You...

26
00:02:09,150 --> 00:02:09,840
Father,

27
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,470
isn't this the path
you wanted me to take?

28
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,080
Now that I've chosen it,

29
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,910
why aren't you happy?

30
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,280
Father is gravely ill.

31
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,630
Prepare another bowl of medicine.

32
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:34,840
Remember,

33
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,310
make sure Father

34
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:38,750
drinks it.

35
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,430
Yes.

36
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,870
You...

37
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,310
You unfilial son!

38
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:55,460
(Zhao Prince's Residence)

39
00:02:55,470 --> 00:02:56,400
Your Highness,

40
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,910
I have an urgent matter to report.

41
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,080
Send her away.

42
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,150
I want to report Li Qingqing.

43
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,600
She's hiding the deposed
Crown Prince, Zheng Yuanhe.

44
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,150
Did you see him clearly?

45
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:12,870
Although it was only his silhouette,

46
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,400
he looked exactly like

47
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,150
the deposed Crown Prince.

48
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:17,710
He's in Li Qingqing's courtyard.

49
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,870
I found it suspicious.

50
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,790
So I rushed here
to report it to Your Highness.

51
00:03:24,100 --> 00:03:26,460
(Qingqing Elegant Courtyard)

52
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:30,800
Search!

53
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:35,800
What are you doing?

54
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:36,910
Miss has just gotten up.

55
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:38,490
She's getting dressed
and can't receive visitors.

56
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,310
You can't...

57
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:53,960
Stop! Yuanhe!
You're going to get a stye!

58
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,910
Don't be angry, Tower Master.

59
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:57,680
I'm here to protect you.

60
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,030
Protect me?

61
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,430
Protect me from what?

62
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,750
Your Highness,
we found nothing suspicious.

63
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,120
Care to explain?

64
00:04:09,130 --> 00:04:10,950
Why did you barge into my room
this early in the morning?

65
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,360
What exactly were you looking for?

66
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,310
Don't sit on my bed.

67
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,230
Please don't be upset, Tower Master.

68
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,000
Ever since Yuanhe burned down the bank,

69
00:04:28,510 --> 00:04:30,040
haven't we still owed

70
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:32,390
our depositors a huge sum of money?

71
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:37,600
Now people are saying
the real owner of the bank

72
00:04:37,610 --> 00:04:39,100
is the Tower Master of Wangshi Tower.

73
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,040
I also heard some desperadoes

74
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,190
have put a huge bounty on your head.

75
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:46,070
I was worried about your safety.

76
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,800
So I came to check on you.

77
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:51,510
That scoundrel Zheng Yuanhe.

78
00:04:51,510 --> 00:04:52,990
Even in death,
he's still causing me trouble.

79
00:04:53,260 --> 00:04:55,000
He got off easy
by falling off that cliff.

80
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,570
Otherwise, I'd have
chopped him into pieces.

81
00:04:58,430 --> 00:04:59,600
Are you sure he's dead?

82
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:05,310
I'm sure.

83
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:12,430
Tower Master, have you come up with any
new money-making ideas lately?

84
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,870
After all, our business
still has to go on.

85
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,800
We still have so many debts to pay off.

86
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,870
Lately, I've been testing
a premium delivery service

87
00:05:19,870 --> 00:05:21,720
among the wealthy ladies.

88
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,240
Once I've worked everything out,

89
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:25,310
we'll open a proper shop.

90
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,510
We'll work on making it
bigger and stronger.

91
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,800
Then we'll pay off all the bank's debts.

92
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:36,680
Then,

93
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:39,600
how about we open
a husband-and-wife shop?

94
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:42,950
Now that Yuanhe is dead,

95
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:44,720
you no longer have to hide.

96
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:47,720
Divorce Pan Yang as soon as possible.

97
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,630
Have you lost your mind?

98
00:05:50,190 --> 00:05:51,190
Get out of here!

99
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,920
You even got my bed dirty.

100
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,600
Could he really be after me?

101
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,160
How is it, Your Highness?

102
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:36,000
I told you

103
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,070
you were mistaken.

104
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:39,070
Qingqing and Your Highness are so close.

105
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,000
Why would she
hide the deposed Crown Prince?

106
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,510
Your Highness,

107
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,870
I was wrong.

108
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:45,070
I misjudged the situation.

109
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:47,390
I won't dare spy on Qingqing again.

110
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,310
No.

111
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,240
Keep watching her.

112
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,720
If Qingqing makes any unusual move,

113
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,040
report it to me at once.

114
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:02,190
Yes.

115
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,190
Tower Master.

116
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:09,070
Zheng Yuanzhao has left.

117
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,920
Luckily, you acted quickly.

118
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,480
You sent the Crown Prince
back to Wangshi Tower first.

119
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,120
Even Wangshi Tower is no longer safe.

120
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,310
Zheng Yuanzhao is no longer

121
00:07:18,310 --> 00:07:20,360
the Second Prince
who only cared about making money.

122
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,390
He'll become another Zheng Yuanhe.

123
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:26,000
He may be even more dangerous than him.

124
00:07:26,510 --> 00:07:27,310
Tower Master,

125
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:29,510
why don't we withdraw with all our men?

126
00:07:29,520 --> 00:07:31,310
Let's go to the western frontier
and find an uninhabited place.

127
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:32,750
We'll build our own city
and make our fortune there.

128
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:33,750
No.

129
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,830
Zheng Yuanzhao deceived me so badly.

130
00:07:35,870 --> 00:07:36,950
If I don't deal with him,

131
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:37,920
I won't have...

132
00:07:38,290 --> 00:07:39,630
worked all this time for nothing.

133
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:40,870
All right.

134
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,390
Whatever you say,

135
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:43,560
I'll do, Tower Master.

136
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:49,310
Go to Dongjin Pier.

137
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,360
Buy a few ships.

138
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,830
Have them sail
into the harbor every day.

139
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,270
Carrying cargo.

140
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,800
Cargo?

141
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,680
Rocks, sand, anything will do.

142
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,040
As long as it looks

143
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,000
busy.

144
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,190
Yes.

145
00:08:04,390 --> 00:08:05,160
Move.

146
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,120
(To deal with Yuanzhao,)

147
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,120
(Zheng Yuanhe is just as crucial.)

148
00:08:47,030 --> 00:08:47,960
Seen enough?

149
00:08:48,270 --> 00:08:49,200
What?

150
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,870
Do I have to pay
to look at my own servant?

151
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,790
Have you finished
the curved plow and the new desk

152
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,750
I asked you to make?

153
00:08:58,620 --> 00:08:59,590
They're in the backyard.

154
00:09:01,550 --> 00:09:04,120
Orders at Wangshi Tower
have surged these past few days.

155
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:06,510
This is the new spinning machine.

156
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,080
The hand-cranked fan.

157
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,510
The rice huller.

158
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:12,150
And this.

159
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,840
The composite crossbow.

160
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:17,670
Finish all of them within three days.

161
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:19,910
Three days?

162
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,550
Even the best craftsmen
in all of Great Yong

163
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:24,670
wouldn't dare promise
to finish them in three days.

164
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,870
I'm not doing it.

165
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:32,790
I'll do it,

166
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,670
but it'll cost extra.

167
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:38,550
So you've learned to bargain now.

168
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,240
Fine.

169
00:09:40,270 --> 00:09:42,270
As long as
you finish everything on time,

170
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:45,750
I'll appoint you
Chief Technical Officer.

171
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,960
Chief Technical Officer.

172
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:49,600
What rank is that?

173
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,910
It's a higher rank than Jiuzhu's.

174
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:54,600
Later, Jiuzhu will take you
to a new place.

175
00:09:54,790 --> 00:09:56,510
From now on,
you won't have to sleep here.

176
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:57,800
You won't have to eat leftovers.

177
00:09:57,960 --> 00:10:00,550
You'll even get ten taels
of pocket money every month.

178
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:03,120
A new place?

179
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:05,910
You're not going?

180
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:07,520
Who are you to tell me what to do?

181
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,120
(Men...)

182
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,990
(Need to be tough
when the time calls for it.)

183
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,630
(And when it's time to soften up,)

184
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:29,720
(a little sweetness is all it takes.)

185
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,970
Don't think I don't know
what you're thinking.

186
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,880
Once I've earned enough money
to buy my freedom,

187
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:38,750
the first thing I'll do
is tear your black shop down.

188
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:42,150
Fine. I'll be waiting.

189
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,910
But before that,

190
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:45,790
you have to finish all these blueprints.

191
00:10:57,870 --> 00:10:58,630
What is it?

192
00:10:58,750 --> 00:10:59,960
Find a new place.

193
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,200
Get Zheng Yuanhe settled there.

194
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:04,360
Neither the Pan Residence
nor Wangshi Tower is safe anymore.

195
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:06,750
Have him hurry up and make what I need.

196
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:08,210
Find someone to keep an eye on him.

197
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:09,120
Understood.

198
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,080
Also,

199
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:12,080
do you know about newspapers?

200
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,320
Of course.

201
00:11:13,510 --> 00:11:16,030
If I asked you
to open a new newspaper office

202
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:17,960
to compete with our Wangshi Chronicle,

203
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:18,870
could you do it?

204
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:21,270
I have plenty of people
who know printing.

205
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:22,870
But when it comes to content,

206
00:11:23,260 --> 00:11:23,960
I'm out of ideas.

207
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,910
Don't worry about the content.

208
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:25,800
I'll take care of that.

209
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,150
Go on. You can name it yourself.

210
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:30,790
Hey!

211
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,510
Can't you walk properly?

212
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:36,300
(Elegance Fills the Garden)

213
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,120
Your Highness.

214
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:37,790
What is it?

215
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:40,960
Our newspaper's sales have stayed
below a thousand copies for days.

216
00:11:41,910 --> 00:11:42,600
Why?

217
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:44,940
(Qingxin Daily)

218
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:46,950
Several new newspaper offices
have opened in the north of the city.

219
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,710
They're using exactly
the same approach as ours.

220
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:51,080
And the Tower Master
hasn't written any new poems,

221
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,670
so our reputation

222
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,790
has plummeted.

223
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:55,870
Didn't I have the Chancellor
of the Imperial Academy

224
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,590
and every year's
top scholar write poems?

225
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,440
What newspaper office

226
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,360
could have talent like mine?

227
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:02,600
They don't seem to be writing poetry.

228
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:04,270
Look at the Qingxin Daily.

229
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:07,030
They're serializing novels
in the newspaper.

230
00:12:07,510 --> 00:12:08,480
What?

231
00:12:08,550 --> 00:12:10,200
(Qingxin Daily)
They're telling stories in the newspaper.

232
00:12:10,210 --> 00:12:11,500
A new installment comes out every day.

233
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,600
(Oath of the Peach Garden, Three Kingdoms)
They keep readers hooked.

234
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,870
If they want to know what happens next,

235
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:16,670
they have to buy the paper every day.

236
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:18,000
Made-up stories

237
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:19,750
are more popular than poetry?

238
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:21,000
Everyone is talking about them.

239
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,390
(Story of the Stone)
The Story of the Stone in Qingxin Daily.

240
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,960
(Three Kingdoms)
Three Kingdoms. Journey to the North.

241
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:24,960
(Journey to the North)
Every one of them is captivating.

242
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,880
They're better
than any storybook in Great Yong.

243
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,000
If this keeps up,

244
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:30,750
our newspaper will become worthless.

245
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,910
The only person who could
have come up with this

246
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:37,270
is her.

247
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,360
Search Wangshi Tower immediately.

248
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:41,200
Yes.

249
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,510
Tower Master.

250
00:12:47,550 --> 00:12:48,670
Yuanhe is here.

251
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:51,870
Quick, help me mess up the room.

252
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,320
Tower Master, what's wrong?

253
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:29,600
Didn't you tell me
to think of a way to make money?

254
00:13:30,670 --> 00:13:33,240
Do you think it's that easy?

255
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:49,390
A next-generation technology platform.

256
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:53,720
What's that?

257
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:56,670
It's a brand-new technology.

258
00:13:57,810 --> 00:13:59,270
Too bad I don't know how to make it.

259
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:06,390
A new issue of Qingxin Daily
has just come out.

260
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:07,960
Have you seen it, Tower Master?

261
00:14:16,850 --> 00:14:20,210
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

262
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:24,370
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

263
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:26,890
♪Your smile♪

264
00:14:27,130 --> 00:14:29,410
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

265
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:33,090
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

266
00:14:33,570 --> 00:14:36,890
♪Yet I stand before you♪

267
00:14:37,610 --> 00:14:41,450
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

268
00:14:41,850 --> 00:14:43,770
♪Though fate tries♪

269
00:14:43,770 --> 00:14:46,370
♪To make us pass each other by♪

270
00:14:46,570 --> 00:14:50,010
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

271
00:14:50,250 --> 00:14:51,890
♪Though time slips by♪

272
00:14:51,890 --> 00:14:53,650
♪As day turns into night♪

273
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:58,210
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

274
00:14:58,610 --> 00:15:01,010
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

275
